fulltitle: Ask the King Ep. 81: May 7, 2020 pt1 - Personal Update, Ubisoft Games, "My Fault"
title: Ask the King Ep. 81: May 7, 2020 pt1 - Personal Update, Ubisoft Games, "My Fault"
description:
Post up your questions for the next episode of Ask the King here: https://thekingofhate.com/forums/topic/5272-ask-the-king-ep-82-july-9-2020/


Topics in this part:
3:45 Health Update
5:00 Public statement about personal stuff (no specifics, but somewhat of an explanation and conclusion)
21:25 What is the "it" factor that Ubisoft open-world games seem to be missing but other games seem to contain?
28:23 What is the biggest thing that you've admitted to being your fault in your life?
36:06 Do people understand what it really means to be a full-time streamer six days a week? How draining is it?
39:45 Will I change the music on my pre-streams?
43:35 Do I think about my days of being a pro-Street Fighter player and have regrets from that period?
48:50 How do I rank the Nioh games in regards to the Soulsborne series?
